lyTime":"2019-02-12T01:29:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"351eb63bfe802ec33e540082220d94460a111bb6","tid":1017920,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T04:07:51.000Z","msg":"近呢半年已經係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d856f71c4300e7d4d91e8cc36b2ec93c3e53ef2a","tid":1017920,"uid":55731,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T02:45:45.000Z","msg":"成日都好攰淨係想訓係張床度<br />\n返緊工個陣就想扒係張枱度<br />\n覺得自己日日都無乜精神咁"},{"pid":"31a8f2d9617102a828af9cb4b6c8005f38ec9378","tid":1017920,"uid":181014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T03:04:24.000Z","msg":"打小d丁啦"},{"pid":"2f8ed7d1bba7c1827b6cae1b1acc12aa29ee7d68","tid":1017920,"uid":200317,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70b7bdd4dc0e7640d97bfb6b2f345bfbeaaa0c34","tid":1017920,"uid":27725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T21:43:22.000Z","msg":"最近成日都好低生產力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定咗嗰日要做嘅嘢好多都做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 明明已經坐咗喺度，已經做緊，但係個人仲係冇咩精神，個腦唔係好郁咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T05:27:09.000Z","msg":"訓教有好多因素 直頭一門學問黎<br />\n仲有覺得質素高ge訓教就好似一個娛樂咁 係享受 <br />\n<br />\n首先<br />\n訓教最重要係<br />\n1) circadian rhythm 就係我地成日講ge生理時鐘<br />\n如果你每日都差唔多時間入睡（起身時間一樣重要D），每日一樣時間起身， 身體會sense到個時間 然後慢慢起你起身前ready<br />\n呢個ready係用你人體ge溫度黎調節(body temperature related to rate of metabolic reaction)<br />\n簡單講 體溫高=多能量output<br />\n體溫低=低output<br />\n<br />\n所以如果固定時間起身 身體就會係起身前提高body temperature,令個人更有精神<br />\n<br />\n2）後續<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我都研究緊訓教<br />\n<br />\n我以前都係無精神，但慢慢查醫學paper<br />\n跟住生理時鐘 實測真係有用<br />\n<br />\n但係其實要持久咁跟住係心理戰<br />\n夜晚望望下電話就過o左訓教時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f523a44a48d75862972ab1c1dbbbec93ed418ff6","tid":1017920,"uid":200317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c1cba488d2d65637b1889d4d41df9796a5d723f","tid":1017920,"uid":27725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7fa0081c351e47954a5e867012a699061cdbf339","tid":1017920,"uid":214997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T21:59:26.000Z","msg":"平時訓幾耐"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T22:02:42.000Z","msg":"9個鐘倒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T05:30:02.000Z","msg":"樓主幾多歲1x 2x?"},{"pid":"976f1ca28547d735e1ff607fd5389548d796db6c","tid":1017920,"uid":29880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T05:30:41.000Z","msg":"我覺得呢啲係心理問題<br />\n當你對人生有希望自然會有動力"},{"pid":"8373f95def754acf5d461869b97568c85df0d769","tid":1017920,"uid":65220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T17:57:30.000Z","msg":"做緊既野都無咩興趣咁?"},{"pid":"403310e39b0b568f12e3afa43812d93e3e74d936","tid":1017920,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T07:29:10.000Z","msg":"好攰，唔想諗野，無晒興趣同埋鬥志<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唉....."},{"pid":"e60d5bacb60db07fa5dca8d9a9fb9a4b24130ee9","tid":1017920,"uid":204429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T07:30:42.000Z","msg":"正常現像黎 樓豬唔洗膽心"},{"pid":"6feacdafeaa57df550a65d4f907590875db43d2f","tid":1017920,"uid":196092,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T08:06:11.000Z","msg":"打丁過度 成日失眠 心情緊張 情緒低落 是但中一樣"},{"pid":"250c320500fa18672dade334c2f157df51efd221","tid":1017920,"uid":196092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T08:07:32.000Z","msg":"仲有 過度睇手機 嚴重既會睇到隻眼仆左街"}]}